# 🌐 Nadeem Najumudeen - Personal Portfolio Website

Welcome to my personal portfolio website! This project is built to showcase who I am, what I do, and how to connect with me. It includes smooth animations, responsive design, a dark/light theme toggle, and interactive features — all crafted with modern web tools.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🌓 **Dark/Light Theme Toggle**
- 🧭 **Smooth Page Transitions**
- 🎯 **Scroll Animations using AOS (Animate On Scroll)**
- 📱 **Mobile-Responsive Design with Hamburger Menu**
- 🧠 **Typing Animation on About Page**
- 🧩 **Accordion Toggle for Skills Section**
- 📇 **Hover-Animated Profile Card**
- 📎 **Professional Contact Section with Icons**
- 🎨 **Gradient Background and Section Styling**
- 📄 **Favicon with ND branding**

---

## 🧱 File Structure

/ (Root)
├── index.html # Homepage with hero and contact section
├── about.html # About me with skills and goals
├── projects.html # Projects (Coming soon)
├── style.css # [Optional] External CSS if used
├── favicon.png # ND icon for browser tab
├── profile.jpg # Circular profile picture for About page
└── README.md # Project info and documentation

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **HTML5** – Structure
- **CSS3 + Tailwind CSS** – Styling & Responsiveness
- **JavaScript** – Interactivity and animations
- **AOS (Animate On Scroll)** – Scroll-triggered animations
- **Icons8** – Platform icons (GitHub, Email, LinkedIn, etc.)
- **GitHub Pages** – Deployment

---

## 💡 Future Improvements

- Add a **Projects** section with interactive cards.
- Improve accessibility with more `aria-label`s and keyboard support.
- Add animations to contact icons on hover.
- Optimize for SEO and performance.

